Joe Absolom https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Absolom 0 Joseph Absolom (born 16 December 1978 in Reading, Berkshire) is an English actor best known for playing Matthew Rose in the popular BBC soap opera EastEnders and Al Large in Doc Martin.
